課程概述 Course Description
       The seniors’ daily activities constitute the six major topics in this undergraduate certificate program. We believe that these activities significantly affect the health and well being of the senior residents and potential business models need to be developed for their special needs. An overview and these topics are presented below.The seniors’ daily activities constitute the six major topics in this undergraduate certificate program. We believe that these activities significantly affect the health and well being of the senior residents and potential business models need to be developed for their special needs. An overview and these topics are presented below.    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
Understanding psychological , psychological and social changes in aginghow these changes present challenges for successful aginghow to make choices 

